entries.title: More social media regulation is coming in 2023, members of Congress say
entries.description: Legislators and advocates say they are looking to further regulate social media companies in 2023.

entries.title: You may not know the difference between 'habits' and 'routines'—and it's your key to success in 2023, says attention expert
entries.description: Nir Eyal, the author of "Indistractable," explains why it's completely fine if your New Year's resolutions never become habits.

entries.title: ‘I work just 5 hours a week': A 39-year-old who makes $160,000/month in passive income shares his best business advice
entries.description: Graham Cochrane went from living on food stamps to making $160,000 a month in passive income through his educational music blog and online courses. He shares his best business advice for new entrepreneurs.

entries.title: Should you get creative with your resume? Experts decide whether you're more likely to land your dream job
entries.description: People are making their resumes look like company’s websites or products. Experts weigh in on whether this helps secure dream jobs.
